videos.description: After Kansas hits a 3 on a possession in the first half, Iowa State answers with one of their own on the next possession.
videos.headline: Jayhawks and Cyclones trade 3s

videos.description: Nick Weiler-Babb hits a big three in the first half as No. 24 Iowa State leads No. 7 Kansas at Allen Fieldhouse.
videos.headline: Cyclones hit big 3

videos.description: Up by 5 points, Nick Weiler-Babb hits a deep 3-pointer that extends Iowa State's lead over Kansas in the second half.
videos.headline: Weiler-Babb drills deep 3 to pad Cyclones' lead

videos.description: Lagerald Vick throws down a monster slam as the Allen Fieldhouse crowd goes wild in the second half.
videos.headline: Vick throws down sick alley-oop

videos.description: Marcus Garrett gets the big and-1 to get the Kansas crowd hyped.
videos.headline: Garrett pulls off big and-1
